      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=12149&rangeEnd=12181",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=12149&rangeEnd=12181"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_4_3070-3091",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3070-3091",
      "markText": "想搞清楚拒绝向混乱低头时，人会变成什么样。",
      "totalCount": 6534,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3070&rangeEnd=3091",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3070&rangeEnd=3091"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_4_1915-1963",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1915-1963",
      "markText": "这个小小的创新承载着他的执念：他的藏品将会免遭混乱的屠戮，下一次混乱来袭时，他的秩序将屹立不倒。",
      "totalCount": 6450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1915&rangeEnd=1963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1915&rangeEnd=1963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_4_978-1003",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "978-1003",
      "markText": "一个聪明人会接受这一事实；一个聪明人不会与之抗争。",
      "totalCount": 6368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=978&rangeEnd=1003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=978&rangeEnd=1003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_9_4997-5055",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4997-5055",
      "markText": "他想到了最有创意的办法：下毒。他在潮汐池里撒下几撮毒药，然后看着水面，很快，一群杜父鱼、海星和鰕虎鱼的尸体浮了上来。",
      "totalCount": 6204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4997&rangeEnd=5055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4997&rangeEnd=5055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_22_1703-1729",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1703-1729",
      "markText": "如果你七岁的孩子问你生命的意义是什么，你会怎么回答？",
      "totalCount": 6200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1703&rangeEnd=1729",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1703&rangeEnd=1729"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_5_1591-1664",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1591-1664",
      "markText": "花时间绘制别人已经画好的地图，就是轻浮之举，是对一日光阴的侮辱；再说，生活于他们而言本就不易，有那么多苹果要摘，那么多土豆要除草，那么多碎布要缝。",
      "totalCount": 5695,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_4_1485-1566",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1485-1566",
      "markText": "几百个罐子在地上摔得粉碎。碎玻璃和倒下的架子让标本支离破碎，空气中弥漫着乙醇的味道。最糟糕的是名字，那些精心摆放的锡牌散落一地，几百条费心命名的鱼重回未知的混沌。",
      "totalCount": 5389,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1485&rangeEnd=1566",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1485&rangeEnd=1566"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300048761_5_4928-4962",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4928-4962",
      "markText": "心理学家研究过这种现象——收藏这一行为在人痛苦时能够带来的甜蜜慰藉。",
      "totalCount": 5376,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300048761&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4928&rangeEnd=4962",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0af32760813ab798cg01135c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4928&rangeEnd=4962"
    },
